text: ( music playing )

I need to find
my missing piece.

♪ And be more than
a mystery ♪
( both grunting )
It's over, Vanna.
Wake up, everybody.

- What happened?
- Mm, wait.
That was crazy.

- Addison, be careful!
- She's after--
The moonstone. I know.

Oh, guys, I just had
the craziest dream.

Vanna was a vampire
and we were all hypnotized
and-- whoa.

She was only using us
to help bring back her family.

Wait, Vanna, wh--
where is your family?

Wasn't this supposed
to wake them up?

I don't know what went wrong.
( sighs )

I guess they'll stay
sleeping forever.

- I'm all alone.
- You're not alone.

I know what it's like
to question who you are
and where you belong and--

and I wouldn't wish that
on anyone.
Don't trust her, Addison.
She hypnotized all of us.

I don't trust her yet,
but I will help her.

I may not know what I am,
but

I know the kind of person
I want to be.

- We've got your back, Addison.
- All of us do.

I may not trust new people,
but I trust you.

Aww, Willa.
( chuckles )

Guys, we're strongest
when we come together.

And when we eat
our vegetables.

That's it.
When we come together.

Remember the first week
at tryouts?

Yeah. It started when you and I
caught Vanna.
You mean when a zombie Z-band

and my moonstone connected with
a vampire's crystal.
On it.

- Whoa.
- Yo.

- ( gasping )
- Whoa.

- Wow.
- Mom! Dad! Baby Vinnie!

- Oh!
- All: Aww.
Guys, this is my family.
Mom, Dad, these are... my--

Friends.
It's so nice to meet you.
Thank you, Addison.

For everything.
You are truly special.

I hope you find out
what you are.

I know exactly
what I am.

- I'm a cheer captain.
- Come on, squad.

We've got a pep rally
to get to.

- ( cheering )
- Come on, guys, let's go.

You ready to watch Addison crush
her first pep rally as captain?
I know I am.
